quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif, Laam, Ra. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwazo n’Imana yonyene gusa). Aya majambo ari muri iki gitabu akoranije ibintu bikenewe vyose, nukuvyerekana neza k’umugaragaro"
  15,2,Kenshi na kenshi bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri bazokwipfuza iyo bobaye aba Isilamu
  15,3,"Nimubareke bafungure kandi binezereze hanyuma bahendwe n’icizero c’ububeshi, mugabo ubu vuba bazotahura"
  15,4,Natwe ntitwahoneje igisagara icarico cose atari uko ico gisagara ikiringo caco categekanijwe
  15,5,"Abantu abaribo bose ntibashobora kuba imbere y’isanganya ryabo, canke ntibashobora guteba mugihe umwanya wabo wageze"
  15,6,"Baravuze bati:- ewe wamanuriwe ubutumwa, mu vy’ukuri wewe uri umusazi"
  15,7,"Mbega\tni\tkuki\tutatuzanira\tabo\tbamarayika\tbokuduhonya\tniyaba\tari mubantu bavugisha ukuri"
  15,8,"Twebwe ntitumanura Abamarayika atari k’ukuri, aho rero ntibazohabwa ikiringo"
  15,9,Mu vy’ukuri nitwebwe twamanuye ubu butumwa ariyo Qur’ani nyeranda kandi mu vy’ukuri nitwebwe tuzoyakingira
  15,10,"Ntankeka\ttwarazanye\tintumwa\tz’Imana\timbere\tyabo\tiri\tmumirwi y’abantu bari imbere"
  15,11,"Kandi\tntibashikiwe\tn’intumwa\ty’Imana\tiyariyo\tyose\tatari\tuko bayikengereye"
  15,12,Ni nk’uku twinjiza mumitima yaba bahakanyi b’Imana
  15,13,Ntibemera ibi vyose mugihe yaho bahitiwe n’uburorero bw’abantu baho hambere yabo
  15,14,Iyo tubugurira abo bahakanyi b’Imana umuryango w’ijuru bakaguma baduga
  15,15,"Rero bari kuvuga bati:- amaso yacu yarozwe, ahubwo twebwe turi mu bantu barozwe"
  15,16,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\ttwashize\tmw’Ijuru\tibituro\tnugushariza\tkubera\tabantu baziraba"
  15,17,Tukaba tuzikingiye n’amashetani aguma yirukanwa
  15,18,"Mugabo\tuwumviriza\tinkuru\tmunzira\tz’ubusuma,\trero\taca\takurikirwa n’igishirira c’umukomezwa kiboneka neza"
  15,19,N’Isi twarayishashe no muriyo tuyishira mwo imisozi nuku nagishamwo ibintu vyose kurugero rwaco
  15,20,Twaraba giriye muriyo ibintu vy’ubuzima bwanyu nivy’ubuzima bwabarya mutunze mwebwe ataco mubaha kubijanye n’imigisha
  15,21,"Ntakintu nakimwe atari uko amamuko yaco ava muri twebwe, kandi ntitukimanura atari kurugero rukwiye"
  15,22,"Kandi tuzana imiyaga yuzuye mwo urume nukumanura amazi y’imvura avuye muri ivyo bicu, hanyuma tukaba nywesha kuriyo kandi si mwebwe muyashiraho"
  15,23,"Ni twebwe turema kandi tukica, natwe ni twebwe basirwa"
  15,24,Kandi turabazi abatangura muri mwebwe kandi turabazi abacererwa
  15,25,"Ntankeka Umuremyi wawe niwe azobegeranya, mu vy’ukuri niyo nyene ubuhizi n’ubumenyi buhagije"
  15,26,"Twararemye ikiremwa muntu tumukuye mw’ivu ryumutse rifise n’ijwi, rivuye muvyondo vyirabura vyavunditswe"
  15,27,"N’ibisigo twabiremye imbere yaho, mu muriro w’umuyaga w’ubushuhe bwinshi cane"
  15,28,"N’Umuremyi wawe igihe yabwira Abamarayika biwe ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nzorema umuntu ndamukuye mw’ivu ryumutse rifise ijwi rivuye muvyondo vyirabura bivunditswe"
  15,29,"Ninaheza kumurema nukumuhuheramwo umutima uvuye iwanje, rero nimu murweko nukumu gamburukira"
  15,30,Rero abamarayika bose hamwe bara gamburuka
  15,31,Dukuyemwo uwitwa Ibilisi niwe yanse kuba hamwe naba gamburutse
  15,32,"Imana yavuze iti:- ewe Ibilisi vyabaye gute kutabaye hamwe naba gamburutse"
  15,33,"Shetani imwishura iti:- jewe sinshobora kugamburukira umuntu waremye mw’ivu ryumutse rifise ijwi rivuye muvyondo bivunze"
  15,34,"Imana ivuga iti:- nuve ngaho mugihe wirukanywe nukuba kure y’imigisha yose"
  15,35,Kandi mu vy’ukuri bizoba kuri wewe harimwo umuvumo kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka
  15,36,"Shetani yishura iti:- Muremyi wanje numpe umwanya kugeza k’umusi bazozurwa abantu bose"
  15,37,"Imana yishura iti:- mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mubaronse ikibanza"
  15,38,Kugeza k’umusi w’umwanya wagenewe ushitse niho uzosandaba
  15,39,"Nayo yishura iti:- Muremyi wanje kubera yuko wanciriye urubanza rw’ukuzimira, nanje nzobaryosha ryosha aba bantu kuri iy’Isi nze ndabazimize bose"
  15,40,Dukuyemwo abantu bawe beranda bisukuye neza naneza
  15,41,"Imana ivuga iti:- iyi nzira yabo niyukuza iwanje kandi igororotse"
  15,42,"Mu vy’ukuri abantu banje, wewe ntabushobozi uzoba ufise kuribo, atari bamwe bagukurikira muri abo bazimiye"
  15,43,Kandi ntankeka umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu nibwo bwicaro bwabo bemerewe bose
  15,44,"Uwo muriro ufise imiryango indwi, no kumuryango umw’umwe hariho ahantu hagabuwe"
  15,45,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tabatinya\tImana\tyabo\ty’ukuri\tbazoba\tbari\tmumirima n’amasoko y’amazi y’umusarara"
  15,46,Nimuyinjiremwo n’amahoro ntangere
  15,47,"Kandi\ttuzokuramwo\tamafundo\tyari\tmubikiriza\tvyabo,\tkandi\tbazoba abavandimwe bakundana bicaye hejuru y’inyegano zacami barabana"
  15,48,"Ntibazo korwako n’ingorane, canke ngo bakurwemwo"
  15,49,Babwire abantu banje yuko jewe mfise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije
  15,50,Mu vy’ukuri ibihano vyanje n’ibihano bibabaza cane bimwe vy’akarorero
  15,51,Kandi ubabwire inkuru z’abashitsi b’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  15,52,"Mugihe binjira munzu yiwe nukumuramutsa bavuze bati:- amahoro y’Imana abe kuri twese, nawe abishura nkuko nyene hanyuma aca avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe turabinuvye"
  15,53,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- ntugire ubwoba twebwe tugufitiye inkuru nziza yuko uzokwibaruka ikibondo gifise ubumenyi buhanitse"
  15,54,"Nawe abishura ati:- munzaniye iyi nkuru mugihe namaze kuba umusaza, none n’iyihe nzira mumpaye y’izi nkuru nziza"
  15,55,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- tuguhaye iyi nkuru nziza y’ukuri, rero ntube mu bantu badebukirwa"
  15,56,"Nawe abishura ati:- ni nde adebukirwa kumigisha y’Umuremyi wiwe atari mu bantu bazimiye"
  15,57,"Yishura ati:- none ico mwipfuza n’igiki mwebwe mwatugendeye"
  15,58,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarungitswe kuri ba bantu bacumuye"
  15,59,"Dukuye mwo abakurikiye intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii), ntankeka twebwe tuzoba rokora uko bangana bose"
  15,60,"Dukuye mwo umukenyezi wiwe, niwe twibaza yuko yoba ari mu bantu bazo kwicara inyuma ya bose"
  15,61,"Izo ntumwa\tmugihe\tzashika\tku\tbantu b’intumwa\ty’Imana\tLutwi\t(iii) bafise ishusho ry’abantu"
  15,62,"Lutwi (iii) yavuze ati:- mu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri mu bantu mutazwi kandi nanje sindabazi"
  15,63,"Baca bishura bati:- twebwe tukuzaniye bimwe muvyo bahora bagirira ko amakenga"
  15,64,"Dushitse iwawe n’ukuri, mu vy’ukuri twebwe turi muba vugisha ukuri"
  15,65,"Rero nugende n’abantu bawe mugice c’ijoro nawe ubakurikire inyuma yanyu ntihagire umwe muri mwebwe ahindukira inyuma, hanyuma mugende mutumbera iyo mwategetswe kuja"
  15,66,Hanyuma tumucira intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) kuri rya jambo yuko imizi yabo izocibwa mugitondo
  15,67,Haca haza abantu bo mugisagara banezerewe
  15,68,"Intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) yavuze iti:- mu vy’ukuri aba n’abashitsi banje ntimuntetereze"
  15,69,Kandi mutinye Imana yanyu ntimunkengere
  15,70,"Bavuga bati:- mbega twebwe ntitwakubujije kwakira abantu"
  15,71,"Yavuze ati:- aba bose n’abigeme banje nimwaba mwebwe muri mubagira ibikorwa"
  15,72,Ndarahiye k’ubuzima bwawe mu vy’ukuri abo bantu bari mububorerwe bwabo bataya taya hirya no hino
  15,73,Mumwanya ibihano biraba fata mugihe izuba ryaseruka
  15,74,"Hanyuma\tduca\ttugira\tivyo\tbisagara\tkuba\thasi\thejuru,\thanyuma tubashungurira imvura y’isegenya irimwo ivyondo vyo mumuriro udahera"
  15,75,"Mu vy’ukuri\tmuri ibi\tvyose harimwo icirwa ku bantu bapima\tibintu n’ibindi"
  15,76,N’ibi bisagara twahoneje biri munzira bacamwo mumwanya wose
  15,77,Ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo icirwa kubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  15,78,Mu vy’ukuri abantu bo mumashamba bari mubahemukiye imitima yabo
  15,79,"Kuri\tivyo\ttwarabahanye,\tn’ibi\tbisagara\tuko\tari\tbibiri\tvyari\tmunzira ziboneka neza"
  15,80,"Ntankeka\tabantu\tbo\tmugisagara\tc’Amabuye\tbarahakanye\tintumwa z’Imana"
  15,81,Twarabahaye impanuro zacu mugabo ntibazitaho
  15,82,Nabo bahora babaza amazu yabo ari mumisozi mumahoro ntangere
  15,83,Rero akaruru k’ibihano karabashikiye mugitondo cakare
  15,84,Ntaco vyabamariye muvyo bahora bagira
  15,85,"Natwe ntitwaremye Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose atari uko ari ivy’ukuri,\tkandi\tntankeka\tumusi\tw’imperuka\tuzoshika,\trero\tnugire c’ikigongwe ciza kuwukugiriye inabi, impembo yanyu muzoyisanga k’umusi w’imperuka"
  15,86,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe muremyi wa vyose kandi niwe afise ubumenyi buhagije
  15,87,"Twaguhaye aya majambo y’Imana meranda uko ari indwi asomwa umwanya uwariwo wose, nukuguha iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ikwiye"
  15,88,"Ntukwege amaso yawe mukuraba muvyo twanejereje imirwi itandukanye yabo bansi b’Imana, kandi ntubagirire agahinda kandi wunamike ibaba ryawe ku bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  15,89,"Kandi uvuge uti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndi mubantu batuza mbonekana neza k’umugaragaro"
  15,90,Nkuko twabamanuriye ibihano bose tubitandukanije mumirwi n’iyindi
  15,91,Abagize iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu kuba ariryo koraniro ry’ububeshi
  15,92,"Nivyo, ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana yuko uko tuzoba baza abantu bose k’umusi w’imperuka"
  15,93,Kuvyo bahora bagira vyose
  15,94,"Rero bimenyeshe ivyo wategetswe kugira, kandi ube kure n’ibikorwa vyabagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu"
  15,95,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\ttwebwe\tturaguhagije\tmukugu\tkingira\tn’ivyo\tbafata minenerwe"
  15,96,"Abagira\tImana\thamwe\tn’izindi\tMana\tz’ibintazi,\trero\tubu\tvuba bazotahura neza"
  15,97,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe turazi neza yuko igikiriza cawe cugarijwe n’ivyo bivugira
  15,98,"Nutakambire Umuremyi wawe hamwe n’ukuyihayaza, kandi ube muba yipfukamira bashize imitwe yabo hasi"
  15,99,"Kandi usenge Umuremyi wawe kugeza aho uzoshikirwa n’urupfu. Igisomwa c’Inzuki.\tIkigabane ca (14). Camanukiye IMakkat. Gifise imirongo"
  16,1,"Itegeko ry’Imana rizoshika, rero ntimuyihimirize kuko niyo yisukuye n’ivyoba bigabanutse vyose hamwe nukuyininahaza kwose nukubayi gereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu vyabo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri"
  16,2,"Ibamanurira Abamarayika hamwe n’ubutumwa kw’itegeko ryayo kubo yishakiye mubashumvyi biwe yuko batuza abantu, atawundi akwiye gusengwa atari jewe jenyene gusa, rero nimuntinye"
  16,3,"Niwe yaremye Amajuru n’Isi bimwe vy’ukuri, ari n’iteka ntangere ry’ukuta gereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu vyabo bahakanyi b’Imana"
  16,4,"Niyo yaremye ikiremwa muntu kw’Ima ry’intanga, mukanya ng’uyo wa muntu yabaye umuntu w’amananiza aboneka neza k’umugaragaro"
  16,5,"Niyo yaremye ibikoko, murivyo muharonkeramwo ubushuhe n’ubundi bumaro n’ibindi navyo mukavyikenurako"
  16,6,Mukanezerwa mugihe muzicuye k’umugoroba nomugihe mubiturukije kuja kurisha mugitondo
  16,7,"Nugutwara amatu yanyu iyajana mubisagara mudashobora kuyashikana atari kumakenga n’igorane zihanitse, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wanyu n’intore cane kandi niyo nyene imigisha ihagije"
  16,8,"N’ibitwazi vyanyu arizo farasi hamwe n’ibimeze nk’ifarasi hamwe n’indogobwe kugira ngo muvyurireko bisharije, none mwebwe muzorema ivyo mutazi"
  16,9,"Ni hejuru y’Imana kwerekana inzira y’ukuri, kuko hariho izindi nzira zitameze neza, rero iyo Imana ibishaka ntankeka yari kubarongora mwese uko mungana"
  16,10,Niyo ibamanurira amazi meza avuye mubicu kuriyo muharonkera mwo ibinyobwa no kuriyo niho hanaga ibiterwa murivyo niho murishiriza mwo ibitungwa vyanyu
  16,11,"Ibanagishiriza ibiterwa vy’ubwoko bwose harimwo imizayituni hamwe n’imitende n’imizabibu hamwe n’ibindi vyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose, ntankeka muri ivyo vyose harimwo ikimenyetso ku bantu biyumvira yuko Imana iriho"
  16,12,"Yarabagamburukije Ijoro n’Umutaga hamwe n’Izuba n’Ukwezi n’Inyenyeri nazone zaragamburukijwe kw’itegeko ryayo, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ikimenyetso ku bantu bafise ubwenge"
  16,13,N’ibi yakwiragije kw’Isi bifise amabara atandukanye mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ikimenyetso ku bantu bumva ubutumwa bw’Imana
  16,14,"Nayo niyo yagamburukije ikiyaga, kugira ngo murico muronke ibifungura bishasha kandi mukure murico ibisharizo mwambara, uca ubona rero ubwato buca muri ivyo biyaga kugira ngo murondere imihezagiro yayo kandi muyikengurukire"
  16,15,"Kw’Isi ishiraho imisozi kugira ngo ntinyigange namwe muri kuriyo, ibashiriraho inzuzi n’amayira kugira ngo mushobore gutumbera"
  16,16,N’ibindi bimenyetso ni kunyenyeri bakurikira inzira zabo
  16,17,"Bati:- umwe arema yoba angana na bamwe batarema, mbega mwebwe bantu ntimwibuka"
  16,18,"Nimwa\tharura\timigisha\ty’Imana\tntimuzo\tshobora\tkuyiharura,\tmu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  16,19,N’Imana irafise ubumenyi bw’ivyo munyegeza hamwe n’ivyo muserura
  16,20,Na barya musenga batari Imana y’ukuri ntanakimwe barema ahubwo nibo baremwe
  16,21,"N’abapfuye\tbatari\tbazima,\tntabumenyi\tbafise\tbwukumenya\tigihe bazozurwa"
  16,22,"Imana yanyu n’Imana imwe yonyene rudende, mugabo bamwe batemera umusi w’imperuka imitima yabo niyo ihakana nabo bagaca bishima"
  16,23,"Ntankeka Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo banyegeza hamwe n’ivyo baserura, mu vy’ukuri ntikunda abishima"
  16,24,"Mugihe babwiwe bati:- Umuremyi wanyu yamanuye iki? nabo bishura bati:- n’amajambo y’ububeshi gusa y’abantu bakera"
  16,25,"Kugira ngo bikorere amatu yabo akwiye yo k’umusi w’imperuka, n’ahantu h’amatu yabamwe babatakaza ata bumenyi bafise nimwumvirize, ayo matu bazoba bikoreye nimabi cane"
  16,26,"Baragize ingeso bamwe bamyeho imbere yabo rero Imana ica isenyura amazu yabo iyata mumishingi nayo ibisenge vy’amazu bibarwako, baca bashikirwa n’ibihano batazi iyo vyavuye"
  16,27,"Hanyuma k’umusi w’imperuka Imana izobatetereza n’ukuvuga iti:- bari hehe bamwe mwahora mugereranya nabo n’ibindi bintu hamwe nanje, rero kuberabo mwahora mutongana nabo, nabo bazovuga bamwe bahawe ubumenyi bati:- mu vy’ukuri ibimaramare hamwe n’agahinda k’uno musi uzoba shikira abahakanyi b’Imana"
  16,28,"Mubo Abamarayika bishe n’abahemukiye imitima yabo rero bazo kwitaba itegeko ry’Imana baze bavuge bati:- ntitwamye tugira amabi ayariyo yose, egome ntankeka Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi buhagije cane kuvyo mwahora mugira"
  16,29,"Kuri ivyo rero nimwinjire mumiryango yo mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu nukwicara muriwo mubuzima bwanyu bwose, n’ubwo bwicaro nabwo n’ahantu habi cane ku bantu bishima"
  16,30,"Mugihe babwiwe bamwe bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri bati:- ni ikihe kintu Umuremyi wanyu yamanuye? nabo bazokwishura bati:- Imana yatumanuriye amahoro hamwe nabagize ibikorwa vyiza ng’aha kw’Isi bazoronka ineza, mu vy’ukuri inzu yo mw’Ijuru niyo nziza cane, kandi niyo nzu nziza yabagamburukira Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  16,31,"Imirima y’ubuzima bwabo bwose bazoyinjiramwo hanyuma haze haracamwo imbere yabo inzuzi z’amazi, muriyo bazoronkeramwo ivyo bipfuza mwo vyose, uko niko Imana iriha abayi gamburukira"
  16,32,"Bamwe Abamarayika bica bari munzira nziza bakavuga bati:- amahoro y’Imana azoba kuri mwebwe, rero nimwinjire mw’Ijuru kubera ivyo mwahora mugira"
  16,33,"Hari ikindi barindiriye abo bahakanyi b’Imana yabo y’ukuri atari uko Abamarayika babashikira canke bashikirwe n’itegeko ry’Umuremyi wawe, nivyaba ari uko bagize bamwe bamyeho imbere yabo, n’Imana ntiyaba hemukiye, mugabo nibo bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  16,34,"Rero bashikiwe n’amabi y’ivyo bagize, baca bakikuzwa n’ibihano bamye bahora bafata minenerwe"
  16,35,"Nayo bamwe bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu bavuga bati:- iyo Imana ibishaka ntitwari gusenga icarico cose atariyo yonyene gusa, haba twebwe canke abavyeyi bacu, canke ntitwari kubuza icarico cose atariyo yonyene, rero nivyaba ari uko bagize bamwe bari imbere yabo, mbega hoba hari hejuru y’intumwa z’Imana atari ugushikiriza ubutumwa buri k’umugaragaro gusa"
  16,36,"Ntankeka twararungitse intumwa y’Imana ku bantu yuko bosenga Imana yabo y’ukuri, nugutandukana na Shetani mubi, rero harimwo muribo abo Imana yarongoye, hakaba n’abandi bari mubuzimire bwatsimbataye kuribo, rero ni mugendere kuri iy’Isi hanyuma murabe ivyabaye kuribo mumpera yabo bantu bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  16,37,"Niwaba ufise ishaka rininiya ryukuba rongora, mugabo Imana ntirongora uwutakaza uwundi, kandi ntibazo baronka abazoba tabara"
  16,38,"Nabo bararahira kw’izina ry’Imana kundahiro ikomeye cane yuko Imana itazozura abapfuye, none ni kuki itobazura nayo ari indagano yategetswe kuriyo mugabo benshi muribo ntavyo bazi na gatoyi"
  16,39,Kugira ngo ibamenyeshe muvyo batumvikanyeko kandi bamenye abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri yuko bari ababeshi
  16,40,Imvugo yacu kukintu dushaka ngo kibe nukukibwira ngo kibe kigaca kiba ubwo nyene
  16,41,N’abimutse kubera Imana yabo y’ukuri munyuma yaho bamaze guhemukirwa ntankeka twebwe tuzobicarika ngaha kw’Isi n’ineza ntangere n’impembo y’umusi w’imperuka nininiya cane iyo boyimenya
  16,42,Bamwe bihanganye n’ukwizera k’Umuremyi wabo
  16,43,"Natwe ntitwarungitse intumwa y’Imana imbere yawe tweretse ubwo butumwa, rero nimubabaze abacibuka mutabizi.\ratari niba\rabagabo mwebwe"
  16,44,"Kubimenyetso biri k’umugaragaro hamwe n’ibitabu, tukaba twakumanuriye ubutumwa kugira ngo usigurire abantu ivyamanuriwe kuribo kugirango biyumvire"
  16,45,Mbega barabemeje muri bamwe bagira ingeso mbi yuko Imana itazoba cinyiza kuri iy’Isi canke batazo shikirwa n’ibihano bivuye aho batazi
  16,46,Canke Imana ntizobafata mukugenda kwabo hirya no hino hanyuma ntibaze bashobore kuyica muminwe yayo
  16,47,"Canke ntizobahana mukubagabanya buhoro buhoro, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wanyu n’intungane, kandi niyo nyene impuhwe zihagije"
  16,48,"Mbega ntibabibona ibintu vyose Imana yaremye mugihe ibitutu vyavyo bikikuje kuva iburyo n’ibubamfu, kandi bipfukamira Imana imitwe yabo iri hasi mugihe bifise ubugamburutsi nyakuri"
  16,49,"Vyose bipfukamira Imana imitwe nayo iri hasi, kubigira mw’ijuru no kw’Isi haba mubikoko hamwe n’Abamarayika nabone batishima"
  16,50,"Batinya Umuremyi wabo ari hejuru yabo, nukugira ivyo bategetswe"
  16,51,"N’Imana yaravumereye iti:- ntimugire Imana ngo zibe zibiri, mu vy’ukuri niwe Muremyi umwe wenyene gusa, rero nimuntinye jewe gusa"
  16,52,"Nirwiwe ibiri mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi,\tn’amasengesho yose akwiriye wenyene gusa k’umisi yose, mbega muzotinya uwutari Imana"
  16,53,N’imigisha yose mufise niyavuye ku Mana hanyuma mugihe muhuye n’ivyago ivyarivyo vyose muca mutakambira kuriyo
  16,54,"Hanyuma ibakuriyeko ivyo vyago vyose, umurwi umwe muri mwebwe uca ugereranya Umuremyi wabo n’ibindi bintu"
  16,55,"Barahakana kuri yamigisha twabahaye, rero nibanezerwe gatoyi, ubu vuba niho muzotahura amabi yanyu"
  16,56,"Nabimwe muvyo twabahaye babashiriraho Imana zabo batazi ivyo bagirirwa, kw’izina ry’Imana ntankeka mwebwe muzobazwa kuvyo mwahora mwadukana navyo"
  16,57,"Begeka ku Mana yuko ifise abigeme, nininahazwe kubwayo mugihe kuribo bishakira abo bikundiye nabo ari abahungu"
  16,58,"Umwe muribo aronse inkuru yukuvuka k’umwana w’umwigeme, uca ubona mumaso yiwe hirabuye nukwuzuramwo agahinda"
  16,59,"Agaca yinyegeza n’abantu kubera iyo nkuru mbi yabwiwe, mbega abane n’ico kibondo kubera agahinda canke amuhambe mw’ivu, nimwumve ubwo bubisha bwabo nayo mategeko yabo"
  16,60,"Imana zabo batemera, Imana yabo y’ukuri hamwe n’umusi w’imperuka barafise uburorero bubi, n’Imana niyo nyene ihayagizwa ry’iteka, kandi niyo ifise ubushobozi n’ubuhizi buhagije"
  16,61,"Mbega iyo Imana ihana abantu kubera ibicumuro vyabo, ntiyosigaje n’igikoko nakimwe kuri iy’Isi, mugabo irabarindiriza kugeza kugihe categekanijwe, hagera ico kiringo ntibashobora kurorezwa n’isaha n’imwe canke ntibashobora kuyitanguzako"
  16,62,"Bayiha Imana muvyo badashaka n’imvugo zabo zivugisha ububeshi yuko bazoronka amahirwe, ntankeka abo bantu babikiwe umuriro udahera nabo bazo wusuzwamwo"
  16,63,"Kw’izina ry’Imana twebwe twararungitse intumwa z’Imana ku bantu babayeho imbere yawe, mugabo Shetani yarabasharijije ibikorwa vyabo, kuri ivyo rero ubu niyo mugenzi wabo, nabo bazoronswa ibihano bibabaza cane"
  16,64,"Ntitwa kumanuriye iki gitabu atari uko wobasigurira muvyo batumvikana ko, hanyuma habe uburongozi n’impuhwe ku bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  16,65,"N’Imana niyo yamanuye amazi avuye mw’ijuru, no kuri iyo Si irayi remurura mugihe yari yarapfuye, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ikimenyetso ku bantu bumva"
  16,66,"Ntankeka no mubikoko harimwo ibitekerezo bininiya kubera mwebwe, kuko tubanywesha mubiri munda zavyo no mubiri hagati y’umwanda wavyo no mumaraso yavyo, hakabamwo amata meza ku bantu bayanywa"
  16,67,"Nomuvyamwa vy’imitende hamwe n’imizabibu nivyo muhingurira mwo ibinyobwa biboreza nukuronkeramwo imigisha myiza, mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo ku bantu bakoresha ubwenge bwabo"
  16,68,N’Umuremyi wawe yarabwiye inzuki yuko zokwiyubakira amazu yazo kumisozi no kubiti hamwe no kubitiba vyubatswe n’abantu
  16,69,"Hanyuma mufungure kuvyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose, kandi uce munzira y’Umuremyi wawe yoroheje gucamwo, hava munda zavyo ibinyobwa bifise amabara atandukanye, murivyo harimwo urukizwa kubantu mu vy’ukuri harimwo ibitekerezo ku bantu bafise ivyiyumviro"
  16,70,"N’Imana niyo yabaremye kandi niyo ibica, no muri mwebwe harimwo abasubizwa mubuzima bubi cane, kugeza naho atamenya n’ikintu nakimwe n’ubwenge yahorana nabwo, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi hamwe n’ubushobozi bukwiye"
  16,71,"N’Imana yarabahaye iteka bamwe muri mwebwe gusumba abandi kubijanye n’imigisha yayo, na bamwe bahawe iyo migisha ntibasubiza iyo migisha yabo kubo batunze n’amaboko yabo y’iburyo, kugira ngo bangane kuri iyo migisha, mbega bahakana imigisha y’Imana"
  16,72,"N’Imana yarabaremeye abakenyezi nkuko namwe mumeze, hanyuma ibahezagira kuva kubakenyezi banyu ibibondo hamwe n’abuzukuru, nukuba hezagira ibintu vyiza vyiza, mbega baremera ibitari ivy’ukuri n’uguhakana imigisha y’Imana"
  16,73,"Nabareka Imana yabo y’ukuri, nugusenga abatabafitiye imigisha nagatoyi, haba iyivuye mw’Ijuru canke ng’aha kw’Isi, kandi ntabubasha bw’ikintu nakimwe bafise"
  16,74,"Ntimugirire uburorero ku Mana, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi, namwe ntanakimwe muzi"
  16,75,"Imana itanga akarorero k’umushumvyi atunzwe na Sebuja nawe ataco yishoboje, n’uwundi nawe tukaba twamuhaye imigisha myiza ivuye kuri twebwe, nawe akaba atanga muri iyo migisha mumwiherero canke k’umugaragaro, none abo bantu barangana ikenguruko ryose ni ry’Imana, mugabo benshi muribo ntavyo bazi"
  16,76,"N’Imana itanga akarorero k’abantu babiri, umwe muribo n’ikiragi adashoboye n’ikintu nakimwe nawe afise ingorane na Sebuja wiwe, kuko aho amweretse kuja nta nakimwe amumarira, mbega uyo muntu angana nurya ategeka ibintu vy’ukuri nawe ari hejuru y’inzira igororotse"
  16,77,"Ntahandi hari amabanga y’Amajuru hamwe n’ibiri kw’Isi atari ku Mana, kandi ntihari kuba ijambo ry’umuhero w’Isi atari uko vyari kuba nkugukoma urugohe canke kuba hafi yaho cane, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubushobozi bw’ibintu vyose"
  16,78,"N’Imana niyo yabakuye munda z’abavyeyi banyu mugihe mutari muzi n’ikintu nakimwe, itako ibaha n’amatwi hamwe n’amaso hamwe n’imitima kugira ngo mushobore gukenguruka"
  16,79,"Mbega ntibabona ingene inyoni zikoreshwa ziri mukirere c’ijuru, rero ntawuzi zitira mukirere kugira ngo ntizikoroke atari Imana yonyene gusa, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo ku bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  16,80,"N’Imana yarabahezagiye amazu yanyu ngo abe aribwo buraro bwanyu kandi ibahezagira amazu y’inshato z’ibikoko mubona yuko yoroshe mugihe c’ingendo zanyu n’igihe c’ukuruhuka kwanyu, no kw’isufi zavyo hamwe no kumoya yazo n’imishatsi yazo, hamwe no kubikoresho bakoresha mugihe kirekire"
  16,81,"N’Imana mubintu yaremye yarabagiriye ibintu bizana igitutu, nukubagirira amazu ari mumisozi, kandi ibagirira impuzu zibakingira ubushuhe, n’impuzu z’ivyuma zibakingira mugihe c’ingwano zanyu, uku rero niko Imana ibakwiriza imigisha yayo kugira ngo muyigamburukire"
  16,82,Nibahakana sikuri wewe atari ugushikana ubutumwa bwawe buri k’umugaragaro
  16,83,"Barafise ubumenyi bw’imigisha y’Imana mugabo barayihakana, kandi benshi muribo n’abahakanyi b’Imana"
  16,84,"N’Umusi tuzorengutsa ivyabona ku bantu bose hanyuma ntibazo kwemererwa kubahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, canke ntibazobwirwa ngo nimusabe ikigongwe"
  16,85,"Na bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo mugihe bazobona ibihano vy’Imana, ntibazo gabanirizwa ivyo bihano, kandi ntibazohabwa ikindi kiringo"
  16,86,"Nayo abagereranije Imana n’ibindi bintu mugihe bazobona abo bagereranije Imana n’ibindi bintu bazovuga bati:- Muremyi wacu, aba nibo bagereranywa bacu b’Imana y’ukuri twahora dusenga aho kugusenga wewe Mana yacu, niho bazobabwira iri jambo abo bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu yuko mu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri ababeshi"
  16,87,"No kuri uwo musi w’imperuka bazokwemera amategeko yose imbere y’Imana, kandi bazokwibagira ivyo bahora badukana navyo"
  16,88,"Abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukuzitira inzira y’Imana, tuzo bongereza ibihano hejuru y’ibindi bihano kubera ubwononyi bwabo"
  16,89,"N’umusi tuzohagarika ivyabona kubantu babo bose bababona kubijanye nabo, hanyuma tukuzane nawewe ube muvyabona hejuru yabo, natwe twakumanuriye iki gitabu gisigura ibintu vyose, kandi kirimwo uburokoke n’imigisha hamwe n’inkuru z’umunezero ku bantu bemeye yuko ari aba Isilamu"
  16,90,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana itegeka ibintu vy’ubutungane, hamwe nukugira impuhwe hamwe nuguha abagenzi, hamwe n’ugutuza abafise umwanda w’amabi n’ubuhemu, kandi ikaba kebura kugira ngo mushobore kumenya nugukurikira"
  16,91,"Nimukwize indagano mutanga kw’izina ry’Imana mugihe muzitanze, kandi ntimuze mudohoke kurizo mugihe mwamaze kuzemeza, mugihe mwamaze kuyigira Imana kuba ariyo cabona canyu, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo mugira vyose"
  16,92,"Kandi ntimube nkawa mukenyezi yaca urunyuzi rwiwe ibice bice mugihe rwari rukomeye, hanyuma mugira indahiro zanyu kuba ariyo nzira zuguhendana hagati yanyu, kubera umurwi umwe w’abantu kuba ariwo ufise ubushobozi gusumba uwundi, mu vy’ukuri Imana iriko irabagerageza muri iyo nzira, kandi ntankeka izobibereka k’umusi w’imperuka kuvyo mwahora mutumvikanako"
  16,93,"N’Imana iyo ibishaka mu vy’ukuri yari kubagira umurwi umwe wonyene gusa, mugabo ireka hakazimira uwo yishakiye, nukurongora uwo yishakiye, mu vy’ukuri muzobazwa kuvyo mwahora mugira"
  16,94,"Kandi ntimugire indahiro zanyu kuba ariyo nzira yuguhendana hagati yany(u, hanyuma ukuguru ntikuze kunyerere munyuma yaho kwari guhagaze neza, n’uguhonja amabi yanyu kubera ukuzitira inzira y’Imana nukuronka ibihano bininiya cane)"
  16,95,"Kandi ntimugurishe indagano z’Imana kukiguzi ataco kimaze, n’ibiri ku Mana nivyo vyiza kuri mwebwe nimwaba mutahura neza"
  16,96,"Ivyo mufise vyose bizohera, n’ibiri ku Mana nivyo bizoramba, mu vy’ukuri twebwe tuzoha impembo zabigumije kuvyo bahora bagira"
  16,97,"Abagira ineza mubagabo no mubagore nabo ari aba Isilamu, twebwe tuzobahindurira ubuzima bwiza nukubaha impembo zabo niniya cane kubera ineza bahora bagira"
  16,98,"Niwaba ushaka gusoma iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu, ni wikingire ku Mana yawe ikurinde na Sheteni yavumwe n’Imana"
  16,99,Mu vy’ukuri Shetani ntabubasha ifise kuri barya bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri n’abizera Umuremyi wabo
  16,100,Ubushobozi bwayo nikuri barya bantu bayigira basoma mbike bayo no hejuru yabagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu
  16,101,"Mugihe duhinduye ijambo ry’Imana kurindi jambo, n’Imana nayo ikaba ifise ubumenyi bw’ivyo imanura, baca bavuga bati:- wewe wiyadukije gusa, mugabo benshi muribo ntabumenyi bafise"
  16,102,"Vuga uti:- Mutima mweranda niwo wamanuye kuva k’Umuremyi wawe w’ukuri, kugira ngo bemeze kuri bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri yuko uburongozi hamwe n’inkuru nziza kuba Isilamu"
  16,103,"Ntankeka turazi neza yuko bavuga bati:- hariho umuntu amwigisha ururimi rw’uwo batumberezako, n’imvugo y’abanyamahanga, n’iyi n’imvugo y’ururimi rw’icarabu rutomoye neza"
  16,104,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe batemera amajambo y’Imana y’ukuri, Imana ntizobarongora, mugabo bazoronka ibihano bibabaza cane"
  16,105,Abadukana ububeshi nibarya batemera amajambo y’Imana y’ukuri abo rero nibo babeshi
  16,106,"Uwuhakana Imana yiwe y’ukuri munyuma yubu Isilamu bwiwe, nuko dukuyemwo uwategetswe nawe umutima wiwe uturuye kw’idini rya Isilamu, mugabo uwugururiye igikiriza ciwe k’ubuhakanyi bw’Imana, abo nibo ishavu ry’Imana rizoba hejuru yabo, kandi bazoronka ibihano bininiya cane"
  16,107,"Ivyo vyose nukubera yuko bakunze cane ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi gusumba ubuzima bwo mw’Ijuru, kandi nuko Imana itarongora abahakanyi b’Imana"
  16,108,"Abo nibo bantu Imana yazivye imitima yabo n’amatwi yabo, hamwe n’amaso yabo, abo rero nibo bibagiwe bimwe vy’ukuri"
  16,109,Ntankeka yuko abo bantu aribo bantu bari muruhombo rwo k’umusi w’imperuka
  16,110,"Hanyuma mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe kuri barya bimutse munyuma yukugira ingorane z’ibihano, hanyuma bakarwanira idini hamwe n’ukwihangana, ntankeka Umuremyi wawe inyuma y’ibi vyose niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  16,111,"Umusi waho umutima wumw’umwe wese uzoshika kwiregura, n’umutima wumw’umwe wese uzorihwa kubikorwa wagize, kandi nabo ntibazo hemukirwa"
  16,112,"N’Imana ibatangirako akarorero kugisagara cari gifise amahoro n’umutekano ntangere, imigisha yaco yagishikira kubwinshi buvuye kumpande zose, mugabo barahakanye imigisha y’Imana, kuri ivyo rero Imana ica irambika ico gisagara impuzu y’ikigoyi n’ubwoba kubera ivyo bahora bagira"
  16,113,"Yarabashikiye intumwa y’Imana ivuye muribo mugabo barayihakanye, rero ibihano vyarabashikiye mugihe bonyene bari bihemukiye kumitima yabo"
  16,114,"Nimufungure kuvyo Imana yabahaye, arivyo vyarekuriwe n’amategeko kandi vyiza, kandi mukengurukire imigisha y’Imana mu vy’ukuri nimwaba muyisenga bimwe biboneka"
  16,115,"Yarababujije gufungura kubikoko vyapfuye vyonyene hamwe n’amaraso, n’inyama z’ingurube hamwe n’ivyabazwe kw’izina ritari iry’Imana, mugabo uwugeramiwe n’ikigoyi canke atiyonkoye kandi atarenze imbibe mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi hamwe n’impuhwe zihagije"
  16,116,"Kandi ntimuvuge kubera ububeshi buvugishwa n’indimi zanyu zivuga yuko:- ibi n’ibirekuriwe n’amategeko y’Imana, nibi navyo ntibirekuriwe n’amategeko y’Imana, rero ntimuze mwadukane n’ububeshi ku Mana, mu vy’ukuri bamwe badukana ububeshi ku Mana ntantsinzi bafise"
  16,117,N’umunezero mukeyi nabo bazoronka ibihano bibabaza cane
  16,118,"N’abayahudi twarababujije kuvyo twababwiye kuva kera, natwe ntitwaba hemukiye ahubwo nibo bonyene bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  16,119,"Hanyuma mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe kuri barya bagize amabi yabo kubujuju bwabo hanyuma bagaca basaba ikigongwe kuri ivyo bagaca bagira ibikorwa vyiza, ntankeka Umuremyi wawe munyuma y’ivyo vyose niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi n’impuhwe zihagije"
  16,120,"Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) yari indongozi nubugamburutsi ku Mana bimwe bikwiye, kandi ntiyari mubantu bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu"
  16,121,"Yarashimira imigisha y’Imana, nukumutora hamwe nuku muyobora munzira igororotse"
  16,122,"Duca tumuha ubugira neza, kuri iy’Isi mu vy’ukuri niwe k’umusi w’imperuka azoba ari mu bantu beranda"
  16,123,"Hanyuma tukwereka yuko ukurikira imigenzo y’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) agamburuka bimwe bikwiye, kandi ntiyari mu bantu bagereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu"
  16,124,"Mu vy’ukuri umusi wa gatandatu wagenywe kubera abatumvikana kuwo musi, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe azocira urubanza ruzoba hagati yabo k’umusi w’imperuka kuvyo bahora batumvikana ko"
  16,125,"Bahamagare munzira y’Umuremyi wawe, ukoresheje ubuhizi n’ubutumwa bwiza, hanyuma uharire nabo munzira nziza, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe afise ubumenyi bw’ukumenya uwatakaye munzira yiwe, nawe niwe abazi abarongotse"
  16,126,"Nimwihorana nimwihore neza naneza nkuko mwabonewe, rero nimwihangana mu vy’ukuri ivyo nivyo vyiza ku bantu bihangana"
  16,127,"Niwihangane, n’uwihangana kwawe ntikube atari kubera Imana gusa, kandi ntugire agahinda kubera abo bantu, kandi ntube mu bantu batuntuye kubeera ingeso zabo bagira"
  16,128,Mu vy’ukuri Imana iri kumwe nabamwe bayigamburukira hamwe n’abagira ineza